             was indicted for <rs id="t18191027-87-off471" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18191027-87-off471" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191027-87-off471" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp>
               embezzling a 1 l. Bank note, and 18 s., which he had received on account of his <rs id="t18191027-87-viclabel472" type="occupation">master</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191027-87-victim982 t18191027-87-viclabel472"></join>, 
                     <persName id="t18191027-87-victim982" type="victimName">
                        Nevill 
                        Smart
                     <interp inst="t18191027-87-victim982" type="surname" value="Smart"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18191027-87-victim982" type="given" value="Nevill"></interp>
